{"tid":543452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你張八達通係中文介面定英文介面?","createTime":"2018-01-28T13:42:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T15:56:21.000Z","uid":64694,"like":3,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ac874511c1cb98378d31e74606fc1a02a8292c6a","tid":543452,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T13:42:57.000Z","msg":"話說呢，其實我張八達通一開始係中文介面嚟，之後有一年要續學生優惠，要填form，唔知佢張form好似有啲反智，要係揀果個選項果度打交叉，有一個位係要揀中文定英文，之後我就係中文果個格打交叉(因為我揀中文，所以要喺中文果個格打交叉)，之後佢唔知係咪以為打交叉係指唔要中文，跟住就係我張卡set咗做英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，之後我張卡就一直都係英文介面，用慣咗就覺得唔錯，因為多數人都係中文介面，我拍卡嘅時候容易啲確認到拍卡果張係我張卡嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你哋張卡又用咩介面?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f58b02886810e663d166ee6ccb4be95d9406ff3","tid":543452,"uid":28599,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T13:44:33.000Z","msg":"咁都要問一餐 <br />\n你都幾撚無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7b80c6dd807609180fe786a54f0f1dc858a1bc","tid":543452,"uid":21423,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T13:44:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"853b6d2ca0dc7b005f7f6d3bca2a218d050fb56e","tid":543452,"uid":43817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T13:45:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da80815e89bac18b1658559a9427859ff5dcd47b","tid":543452,"uid":20916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f58b02886810e663d166ee6ccb4be95d9406ff3","tid":543452,"uid":28599,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T13:44:33.000Z","msg":"咁都要問一餐 <br />\n你都幾撚無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T13:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b44abbc8173da50ea98ddc1b88320e463681326",